{{- $renderAsVerification := and .TransientPayload (index .TransientPayload "render_as_verification") -}}
{{ if $renderAsVerification }}{{ if and .TransientPayload (index .TransientPayload "profile_name") }}Dear Mr./Ms. {{ index .TransientPayload "profile_name" }},{{ else }}Dear Valued Customer,{{ end }}

{{ if and .TransientPayload (index .TransientPayload "action_description") }}We have received a request to {{ index .TransientPayload "action_description" }}.

For security, please confirm by entering the One-Time Password (OTP) below in the LIFE AI app:
{{ else }}We have received a verification request from {{ .Tenant }}.

For security, please confirm by entering the One-Time Password (OTP) below in the LIFE AI app:
{{ end }}
{{ else }}안녕하세요, 고객님,

인증을 위해 {{ .Tenant }}에서 발송한 다음 일회용 비밀번호(OTP)를 사용해 주세요:
{{ end }}

{{ .RegistrationCode }}

{{ if $renderAsVerification }}Your OTP will be valid for {{ .ExpiresInMinutes }} minutes.
Do not share this OTP with anyone.

If you did NOT initiate this request, please ignore this email and contact us immediately at support@lifenetwork.ai or change your password right away.

Thank you for trusting LIFE AI!

Best regards,
LIFE AI Team{{ else }}OTP는 {{ .ExpiresInMinutes }}분 동안 유효합니다.
이 OTP를 다른 사람과 공유하지 마세요. {{ .Tenant }}는 계정 보안을 매우 중요하게 생각합니다.{{ end }}
